  "summary": "Editable D2 JSON draft for human review.",
  "general_information": "The CMA CGM Pregolia is a feeder container ship designed by Shanghai Merchant Ship Design & Research Institute (SDARI) and built by JinHai Intelligent Manufacturing Co. Ltd. It has a capacity of 2,487 TEU, with 916 under deck and 1,571 on deck. The vessel is equipped with hybrid scrubbers to meet SOx emission limits and has a 700m^3 sludge water storage tank for waste water management. It also features ice-class navigation and winterization measures for operation in the Baltic region.",
